  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>No More</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Why just the other day </l>
          <l>Destroyed your Book, page by page </l>
          <l>"catharsis" doesn't even begin to describe </l>
          <l>The feeling that it left inside me </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Prayer is a four-letter word </l>
          <l>When I scream and shout and start to curse </l>
          <l>It's pure and frightening what I have got to say </l>
          <l>But You can take it any way </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Break down all of the borders that I see </l>
          <l>Shut out all of the fear and misery </l>
          <l>I don't need it anymore </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>Went to the Wall tonight </l>
          <l>And it was You I had in sight </l>
          <l>Just closed my eyes and let You wash over me </l>
          <l>Enjoying what it means to be free </l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Break down all of the borders that I see </l>
          <l>Shut out all of the fear and misery </l>
          <l>I don't need it anymore</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
